description:
In this karaoke version of "Tell Me The Story of Jesus," you'll be singing along to a classic hymn about Jesus Christ. This song is perfect for any worship service or holiday party!

Whether you're an amateur or a professional singer, this karaoke version of "Tell Me The Story of Jesus" is sure to be a hit. With easy to follow chord changes and a professional recording, this song is perfect for any gathering!

Title :  Tell Me the Stories of Jesus
Author : William H. Parker (1885)
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters youtube channel

chapters.title: TELL me the story of Jesus.
Tell how the angels in chorus
Glory to God in the highest
How He was tried and was tempted
Tell of the years of His labours
Tell me the story most precious
Tell of the grave where they laid Him
Love, in that story so tender
Stay, let me weep while you whisper
